{"tid":2087504,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"繼續Fiester研究，得兩首歌居然打咗去歐美市場","createTime":"2020-06-30T16:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T09:59:36.000Z","uid":186882,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec0a60e9eca29be8c685fc5725f7707b5807266","tid":2087504,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"上次一首秋去冬來，又係幾日爆10K view<br />\n而吸引我注意既係比我碌到fb有佢哋既MV以廣告形式出現喺我面前<br />\n至今3個月都已經去到43k view<br />\n對一隊香港indie band黎計成績已經算好好<br />\n(香港indie band紅起咗既instinct of sight首light一年先得39k view咋）<br />\n<br />\n都印證即使係indie, 有廣告都係會唔同d<br />\n<br />\n至於今次首Mani said<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7rQ6avXzTYE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7rQ6avXzTYE&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=a96a5fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7rQ6avXzTYE</a><br />\n<br />\n一星期已經去到19k view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而下面d留言都同秋去冬來完全唔同，仲多過之前<br />\n而且變撚哂做英文<br />\n當然啦，今次英文歌嘛<br />\n<br />\n但有一個留言我留意到:<br />\n'Instagram ad brings me here'<br />\n<br />\n換言之，今次係IG廣告食中target<br />\n<br />\n而且今次Mani said比之前紅得更加快<br />\n食到歐美市場條水。<br />\n<br />\n證明咗幾樣野<br />\n歐美普遍鍾意呢類女聲Alt metal<br />\n想紅要識落廣告<br />\nMV要拍得靚要有靚既女vocal<br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣好緊要，cls (comments, like, share）<br />\n外國人對呢三樣野比較不吝嗇<br />\n<br />\n最後就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">到而家都未有一句英文comments話佢哋mixing差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n呢樣野香港人真係要檢討，太鐘意搵野屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb935c9b499658dfdd4ac92d9f5f75dbc64aaadf","tid":2087504,"uid":55800,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:28:36.000Z","msg":"咁佢哋啲歌mixing真係做得麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話主流歌手 就算拎去同其他indie band比 都係差一截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都認同佢哋嘅marketing係值得其他獨立樂隊借鏡嘅"},{"pid":"0f084e1b4d366296bd29eb74bd44c4225ac700a8","tid":2087504,"uid":284304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:31:19.000Z","msg":"我撳一個掣就開啟到歐美市場"},{"pid":"9753265792240611b1b0eb3b38a577d946e7da81","tid":2087504,"uid":164185,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0f084e1b4d366296bd29eb74bd44c4225ac700a8","tid":2087504,"uid":284304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:31:19.000Z","msg":"我撳一個掣就開啟到歐美市場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:37:54.000Z","msg":"但買views買成堆假ac留言之後加個打手開post就去左歐美市場核突左d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab04ecef1dfddfe53329db9ea4edd3d231751dfc","tid":2087504,"uid":193514,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:27:09.000Z","msg":"幾萬VIEWS比你吹到上天<br />\n你係brian cha?"},{"pid":"1ca7c621a7fac3567725af0d9d727b12ad34627c","tid":2087504,"uid":186882,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ab04ecef1dfddfe53329db9ea4edd3d231751dfc","tid":2087504,"uid":193514,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:27:09.000Z","msg":"幾萬VIEWS比你吹到上天<br />\n你係brian cha?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:17:56.000Z","msg":"幾萬view對indie黎講好撚多架喇，仲要幾日<br />\n好多出名既indie band擺幾年都無<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我唔係吹奏Fiester好唔好聽又或者廣告抵唔抵買<br />\n而係探討本地音樂做宣傳既可行方法。"},{"pid":"14649e6b7e8c6876f83645a7041dd5b83cd955f9","tid":2087504,"uid":193514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca7c621a7fac3567725af0d9d727b12ad34627c","tid":2087504,"uid":186882,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ab04ecef1dfddfe53329db9ea4edd3d231751dfc","tid":2087504,"uid":193514,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:27:09.000Z","msg":"幾萬VIEWS比你吹到上天<br />\n你係brian cha?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:17:56.000Z","msg":"幾萬view對indie黎講好撚多架喇，仲要幾日<br />\n好多出名既indie band擺幾年都無<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我唔係吹奏Fiester好唔好聽又或者廣告抵唔抵買<br />\n而係探討本地音樂做宣傳既可行方法。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202